      "title": "All three support Dallas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Three independent members of parliament have decided to support the candidate for the mid-term presidential election, Dulas Alagaperuma.",
        "Members of Parliament Vimal Weerawansa, Udaya Kammanpila and Vasudeva Nanayakkara have decided in this way. In this regard, it was officially announced at the press conference held today (19)."
